GHAFAS, a GTK+ client to query train connections & fares
Copyright 2007 tomfuks <xxxxxxxxxxxx>

Parts of the GUI code are taken from Sonata.
The client makes heavy use of ClientForm and BeautifulSoup.


REQUIREMENTS:
	(Required) PyGTK 2.6.0 or newer
	(Required) GTK 2.6.0 or newer

INSTALLATION:
	Just run 'python2.5 setup.py install' as root.

FEATURES:
	+ query connections over an arbitrary timeframe
	+ automatically show availability saving fares
	+ command line control
